title: 'First copy.'
body: I don't mind wearing a first copy sneakers but this one...arrgggh! the logo is a little messed up. When I first bought it i didn't notice so I wore it to a gym. Long story short, There's this hot chick at the gym, she was checking me out from head to toe. I went home and for some reason I took a close look at my sneaker and viola! One pair of the sneaker logo looked like a Cat ran over by a car. How embarrassing! Otherwise the sneaker looked really good and feel light. Now, since I have worn it once i won't be able to return it. Anyway, If you're not very self-conscious like me and would not mind a minute mistake in the logo. Go for it. It's worth the money. There might not even be same error on other pairs.
